Definition: a genus of herbs belonging to the family Boraginaceae that grow in temperate regions and have blue or purple flowers shaped like funnels
Synonyms: genus_Mertensia, plant_genus, family_Boraginaceae, m, a, genus, of, herbs, belonging, to, the, family, Boraginaceae, that, grow, in, temperate, regions, and, have, blue, or, purple, flowers, shaped, like, funnels
Category: noun.plant
